name: PHASE02_LARVA: “Oblivious Genesis”
description: GUIDE TO THE COMPLETE METAMORPHOSIS OF THE MODERN WORLD ENDER. ‘Oblivious Genesis’ showcases the emergence of the monster. Genesis refers to the beginning of something while oblivion is its antonym. The creature is born only to destroy. Nobody in this world is aware of this, they are oblivious to the genesis.
